#### ACTIVE
The weapon active cd, charge, and effects are based on the wielder. If wielder has Mutual Regen tag, Lightning DMG +30%. Planar Armament equip bonus: 
- When you are the leader, after you cast Combo ATK, on the next Stellar Outburst, initial sp is increased by 10% of max sp.
- Upon casting Ult Finisher, trigger 1.5s time stop.

#### PASSIVE 1
Total DMG **+35% (v2) > 20% (v3).** Planar Armament equip bonus: 
- Team Elemental and Physical DMG +12%.
- When AR is activated: Self Lightning DMG +30%, team Total DMG +12%.

#### PASSIVE 2
Enemies take 25% more **Total DMG(v2) > Lightning DMG (v3)** from the wielder. Planar Armament equip bonus: 
- Team Total DMG +10%, Elemental DMG +15%.

#### SYNERGY
Enemies take 2 / 4 / 6% more Total DMG (independent, cannot stack).

Planar Armament equip bonus: Enemies take 2 / 4 / 6% more Lightning DMG from wielder (independent, cannot stack).


