#### TOP
Lightning DMG **+40% (v2) > 30% (v3)**. Planar Armament equip bonus: 
- Characters with [Raise the Banner] gain Total DMG +20%.

#### MID
Total DMG resistance +25%. Planar Armament equip bonus:  
- Characters with [Raise the Banner] gain Physical and Elemental DMG +25%.

#### BOT
Total DMG +25% . Planar Armament equip bonus: 
- Enemies take 18% more Physical and Elemental DMG from characters with [Raise the Banner].

#### 2PC
Lightning DMG **+40% (v2) > 35% (v3).** Planar Armament equip bonus: 
- Enemies take 30% more Lightning DMG.
- When AR is activated: Enemies take 20% more Elemental DMG from characters with [Raise the Banner].
- When LoA is activated: During AR Charging, team Total DMG **+27% (v2) > 12% (v3)**, and enemies take 25% more Total DMG from characters with [Raise the Banner], and characters with [Raise the Banner] gain Physical and Elemental DMG **+20% (v2) > 15%. Self Total DMG +8% (v3)**.
- When LoA is activated: During Stellar Outburst, team Total DMG **+37% (v2) > 22% (v3)**, and enemies take 35% more Total DMG from characters with [Raise the Banner], and characters with [Raise the Banner] gain Physical and Elemental DMG **+25% (v2) > 20%.  Self Total DMG +8% (v3)**.

#### 3PC
Ult and Combo ATK gain Total DMG +15%. Planar Armament equip bonus: 
- When Ult or QTE hits a target, or upon activating Stellar Outburst, or when entering battle as leader, team gain [Raise the Banner] for 25s, can be refreshed.
-  **~~Enemies take 22% more Total DMG.~~ (V3)**
-  When Heavenly Grail is activated:
    - Characters with [Raise the Banner] gain Elemental DMG +20%, Physical DMG +12%, Total DMG +15%.
    - Enemies take 10% more Total DMG from characters with [Raise the Banner]. **If you are the leader +11% more. (v3)**
    - During SO: Enemies take 12% more Total DMG, Physical, Elemental DMG from characters with [Raise the Banner] **and Mutual Regen tag (v3)**.